entries.journal_entry_description: Lt. Cope wants you to follow up on your investigation of the Chirq Council in Doaba Guerfel. Speak with Captain Vitala Baize of CorSec for more details.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go speak with Captain Vitala Baize in Doaba Guerfel.
